        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWeird that after applying this patch helm upgrade fails for AAI.  I am not sure what in this patch is causing it since it is all configmaps changes.\n\nThere is a long gross error but the jist of it is: \n\nError: UPGRADE FAILED: Job.batch \"aai-aai-graphadmin-create-db-schema\"\nis invalid: spec.template: Invalid value: core.PodTemplateSpec {\n....\n....\n\nfield is immutable\n\n\nto reproduce..deploy aai without this patch,\n-cherry-pick it, re-make the aai chart \n-upgrade the existing release with the newly built one that includes this change..\n-see it fail.\n\nPurging and re-installing works fine....Waiting to hear back from you folks before proceeding with this one..",
        "patchset_number": 1
